content.value:
Dinner time. Eating sloppy burritos. 

She: “oh no I dribbled”

Me, using what I and I alone think of as my sexy voice: “want me to clean it up? We all dribble a little meat sauce from time to time.”

We: …

And now not only am I not horny, I’m no longer hungry.
